00:30:59.540 --> 00:31:00.540
que somos,

00:31:00.540 --> 00:31:01.960
señor Lin Heng.

00:31:04.000 --> 00:31:05.580
Ya que me hiciste una pregunta,

00:31:06.120 --> 00:31:06.870
